  "name": "Sacred Defense",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You call upon your deity to grant you their protective blessing. Attempt a @Check[type:religion|dc:30] check. If you have legendary proficiency in Religion, you can instead attempt a @Check[type:religion|dc:40] check to increase the temporary Hit Points you gain on a successful check to 15 (25 on a critical success).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You gain 10 temporary Hit Points. You lose any remaining temporary Hit Points after 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> You gain 5 temporary Hit Points. You lose any remaining temporary Hit Points after 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your deity withholds their blessing. You cannot attempt to call to your deity again for 1 day.</p>"
